data.name: 80:Description,mstelco_PlaceManagement
data.value: This model-driven application provides tracking for all of the physical locations across a service provider’s network. It supports the geographic mailing addresses for residences, multi-dwelling apartment buildings, and commercial and retail areas as well as support for describing regions and polygons through geocoded map points. Additional handling for tracking the locations of and segmenting network and plant resources, regional operating centers, service technology, and the movement of equipment. The app integrates with Azure Maps API for Address lookup and normalization.
data.comment: 'mstelco_PlaceManagement' : Description for AppModule
